{"tid":927311,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IZ*ONE所屬成員將「參與HKT48日本演唱會」卻讓網友超生氣","createTime":"2018-12-04T05:38:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T09:57:12.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1949695a8b51d18524b29ce440f4b88e7f4881e2","tid":927311,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T05:38:49.000Z","msg":"雖然是很有意義的場合但真的跟之前說的不符啊...<br />\n稍早IZ*ONE所屬經紀公司Off The Record娛樂針對先前傳出成員宮脇咲良、矢吹奈子兩人會參與HKT48八周年紀念演唱會的事件發表官方立場做出回應<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.wishnote.tw/550/2018/12/04/550_1366432_1543890469.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2018%2F12%2F04%2F550_1366432_1543890469.webp&h=21b46e71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《Produce48》作為最後選上出道組的日本成員宮脇咲良、矢吹奈子、本田仁美三位成員在由宮脇咲良擔任Center，矢吹奈子、本田仁美擔任前排站位的AKB48第54張單曲《NO WAY MAN》後暫停AKB48家族活動，專注IZ*ONE團體活動<br />\n<br />\n然而卻傳出宮脇咲良、矢吹奈子將參與HKT48即將在15號舉行的八周年紀念演唱會，隨即引起網友高度討論<br />\n<br />\nIZ*ONE粉絲認為兩位成員參加HKT48演唱會的這個舉動，違背了之前發表將專任於IZ*ONE的立場<br />\n<br />\n許多網友也質疑是不是日本成員往後都能兼任兩團的活動，這樣就與之前發表的專任立場完全不符，因此多數人反對兩人參與HKT48演唱會<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.wishnote.tw/550/2018/12/04/550_1366429_1543891438.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2018%2F12%2F04%2F550_1366429_1543891438.webp&h=e6ebe5ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIZ*ONE所屬經紀公司Off The Record娛樂則在今早針對此事回應「兩人參與HKT48演唱會是為了祝賀HKT48誕生八周年，會參與部分舞台演出，不代表也不會有任何兼任活動的事情發生」<br />\n經紀公司最後也針對此事造成大眾困擾道歉並再提到 宮脇咲良、矢吹奈子、本田仁美三名成員作爲組合IZ*ONE的成員進行活動期間將不會再有任何AKB集團的活動安排"},{"pid":"b47f07aa13def817a35fc1038f72b5d00c61b427","tid":927311,"uid":213300,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T05:39:55.000Z","msg":"同之前火箭少女同wjsn case差唔多?"},{"pid":"6308de0b4335a906c50a3f4291cccba09b427ec0","tid":927311,"uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b47f07aa13def817a35fc1038f72b5d00c61b427","tid":927311,"uid":213300,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T05:39:55.000Z","msg":"同之前火箭少女同wjsn case差唔多?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T05:44:44.000Z","msg":"假專任LO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支那人個單大D<br />\n但長久落去E個CASE唔知會唔會做壞規矩"},{"pid":"db6c58292a6f432f3652b82bf88c04d31cca73e0","tid":927311,"uid":2781,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T05:54:33.000Z","msg":"izone咁少活動咪阻住人接job啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc265857d02307bb9a0668c19a635b4a6cd49a4","tid":927311,"uid":74065,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db6c58292a6f432f3652b82bf88c04d31cca73e0","tid":927311,"uid":2781,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T05:54:33.000Z","msg":"izone咁少活動咪阻住人接job啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T06:33:54.000Z","msg":"岩出道黎講 活動已經唔算少<br />\n你重要準備年尾D STAGE<br />\n練習 同 下一次CB呢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4b8667e511cc96b222ea1b720800f8c416b1bb","tid":927311,"uid":46435,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T06:58:22.000Z","msg":"支持日本妹翻日本發展 泡菜收皮啦 霸住啲女想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca73277f74294571e6c8ea2ddba6ceff18d2971f","tid":927311,"uid":52073,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T06:58:41.000Z","msg":"抄twice"},{"pid":"37835d2a92a312b384bd4369a9734a11de2e4c10","tid":927311,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca73277f74294571e6c8ea2ddba6ceff18d2971f","tid":927311,"uid":52073,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T06:58: